                    ANSIBLE-PLAYBOOKS
            .....................................
Playbooks are the files where Ansible code is written. 
Playbooks are one of the core features of Ansible and 
tell Ansible what to execute. They are like a to-do list 
for Ansible that contains a list of tasks. Playbooks 
contain the steps which the user wants to execute on a 
particular machine.Ansible-playbooks are written using 
yaml(yet another markup language).

Execute an ansible-playbook
...........................

ansible-playbook name.yaml

Execute ansible-playbook as root user
.....................................

ansible-playbook -b name.yaml
